CBRE is pleased to offer for lease 49 Stockdale Road, O’Connor.
Strategically Located in the heart of the O'Connor Industrial Precinct with great access to Stock Road, South Street and Leach Highway.

This Large Industrial warehouse benefits from multiple access points via 4 Large Roller doors coupled with outside laydown or storage.

Property Features:
•	Total building area: 4,411sqm*
•	Warehouse area: 4,291sqm*
•	Office: 120sqm*: Separate office area with reverse cycle air-conditioning, shower, and toilet facilities
•	3 Phase power throughout 
•	Large power supply
•	4 x roller doors
•	Good truck access
•	Ideal for Storage, Logistics or Engineering

*approx

Located in O'Connor Industrial precinct. Well positioned to Perth's road network and close proximity to Fremantle Port. The site has 3 street frontage providing ample circulation/laydown and hardstand areas.

The warehouse provides flexibility and has overhead gantry cranes. This facility is highly functional and presents to a high standard.

Warehouse: 3,210.7sqm
Office/Amenities: 580sqm
Total Hardstand: 9,046 sqm
Total Site Area: 15,807sqm

RENTAL $400,000 plus GST & Outgoings

Sites like this one rarely become available and will suit national uses.

For further information or to arrange an inspection, please contact the exclusive leasing agents.
